data.description: Nested on a spacious 5,000 square feet lot, this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home boasts 1,686 square feet of comfortable living space. Featuring a convenient 2-car garage, with plantation shutters throughout the house, it offers both practicality and style. The extended cement driveway accommodates extra parking needs seamlessly. Recently renovated, the addition of a new porch and gazebo enhances the home's appeal, perfect for hosting family gatherings or enjoying peaceful evening outdoors. With its well-designed layout and thoughtful upgrades, this residence promises a delightful blend of functionality and leisure, creating an inviting haven for its fortunate inhabitants. Owned solar to be assumed by the buyer.
